{"results":[{"aya":"029","id":1831,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"当我把它塑成，而且把我的精神吹入他的塑像的时候，你们应当对他俯伏叩头。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"030","id":1832,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"随后，天神们一同叩头，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"031","id":1833,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"唯独易卜劣厮不肯叩头。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"032","id":1834,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"主说：易卜劣厮啊！你怎么不叩头呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"033","id":1835,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"他说：你用黑色黏土塑成人像而创造的人，我不该向他叩头。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"034","id":1836,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"主说：你从这里出去吧。因为你确是被放逐的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"035","id":1837,"locale":"zh","sura":"015","text":"你必遭诅咒，直到报应日。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":15,"previousPage":"/zh/s015-4.json","nextPage":"/zh/s015-6.json"}}